<h1>⏰ Lease Expiration Notice</h1>

<p>Hello {{tenantName}},</p>

<p>We wanted to give you advance notice that your lease at
	<strong>{{propertyAddress}}</strong>
	will be expiring soon.</p>

<div
	style='background: #fef3c7; border: 1px solid #f59e0b; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; text-align: center;'
>
	<h2 style='color: #92400e; margin-top: 0;'>📅 Important Dates</h2>
	<div style='font-size: 18px; margin: 10px 0;'>
		<strong>Current Lease Expires:</strong><br />
		<span style='font-size: 24px; color: #92400e;'>{{formatDate
				expirationDate
				'MMMM D, YYYY'
			}}</span>
	</div>
	<div style='font-size: 14px; color: #78716c;'>
		({{daysUntilExpiration}}
		days from today)
	</div>
</div>

<h2>🤔 What Are Your Plans?</h2>

<p>We'd love to know your intentions so we can plan accordingly. Here are your
	options:</p>

<div style='display: flex; gap: 10px; margin: 20px 0; flex-wrap: wrap;'>
	<div
		style='flex: 1; min-width: 200px; background: #ecfdf5; border: 1px solid #10b981; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px;'
	>
		<h3 style='color: #065f46; margin-top: 0;'>✅ Renew Your Lease</h3>
		<p style='font-size: 14px;'>Stay another year with updated terms</p>
		<div style='text-align: center; margin: 10px 0;'>
			<a href='{{renewalLink}}' class='button success'>Renew Lease</a>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div
		style='flex: 1; min-width: 200px; background: #fef3c7; border: 1px solid #f59e0b; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px;'
	>
		<h3 style='color: #92400e; margin-top: 0;'>📋 Month-to-Month</h3>
		<p style='font-size: 14px;'>Continue with flexible monthly terms</p>
		<div style='text-align: center; margin: 10px 0;'>
			<a href='{{monthToMonthLink}}' class='button warning'>Go
				Month-to-Month</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

<div
	style='background: #fee2e2; border: 1px solid #f87171; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;'
>
	<h3 style='color: #dc2626; margin-top: 0;'>📦 Planning to Move?</h3>
	<p>If you're planning to move out, please let us know as soon as possible:</p>
	<ul>
		<li><strong>30 days notice required</strong> for lease termination</li>
		<li><strong>Move-out inspection</strong> will be scheduled</li>
		<li><strong>Security deposit</strong> process and timeline</li>
	</ul>
	<div style='text-align: center; margin: 10px 0;'>
		<a href='{{moveOutLink}}' class='button danger'>Give Move-Out Notice</a>
	</div>
</div>

<h2>💰 Renewal Benefits</h2>

<p>Here's why staying makes sense:</p>
<ul>
	<li><strong>Avoid Moving Costs</strong>
		- Save thousands on deposits and moving expenses</li>
	<li><strong>No Application Fees</strong>
		- Skip the hassle of finding a new place</li>
	<li><strong>You Know Your Home</strong>
		- Stay in the neighborhood you love</li>
	<li><strong>Preferred Tenant Status</strong>
		- Priority for maintenance and upgrades</li>
</ul>

<div
	style='background: #e0f2fe; border-left: 4px solid #0288d1; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0;'
>
	<p><strong>💡 Good News:</strong>
		As a valued tenant, we're offering competitive renewal terms. Check out
		your personalized renewal offer in your portal!</p>
</div>

<h2>📞 Questions? We're Here to Help</h2>

<p>Your property manager {{landlordName}} is available to discuss:</p>
<ul>
	<li>Renewal terms and options</li>
	<li>Any improvements or repairs you'd like to see</li>
	<li>Move-out procedures if you're planning to leave</li>
	<li>Timeline and next steps</li>
</ul>

<div style='text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;'>
	<p><strong>Please respond by
			{{formatDate responseDeadline 'MMMM D, YYYY'}}</strong></p>
</div>

<p>We hope you'll choose to stay, but whatever you decide, we're here to make
	the process smooth and easy.</p>

<p><strong>{{landlordName}}<br />
		Your Property Management Team</strong></p>